<br>
If I go to an under-30's zone, I try not to stop moving, hehe.<br>
<br>
My pet peeve is melee types who moan for heals because they've been soloing and are low on health.  HEY GUYS - GET A CLUE: GROUP WITH A HEALER.  Why should I spend my mana healing you so you can run out and level while I sit on my butt?  Fortunately shaman are pretty good soloers, but I can see a lvl 30 cleric being really PO'd by this behavior.<br>
<br>
BTW, any cleric or chanter gets a cheerfully delivered set of buffs any time they look like they need 'em.  I've had enough free resurrections and free clarity from nice toons to cover that.<br>
<br>
